0.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/yoi1665702919920.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/yoi1665702919920.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"yoi1665702919920\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"yoi1665702919920__uniface_glyphs_524470\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Uniface delivers a set of glyphs for use in its own tools and editors. New glyphs are added in each new version of Uniface, sometimes replacing older glyphs, sometimes as additions.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"yoi1665702919920__p_d177449e1_d177450e1_d177451e1\">The following topics list many of the glyphs delivered\n      with Uniface from Uniface 7, 8 and 9. Each topic lists the glyphs alphabetically by name.</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"yoi1665702919920__ul_n51_1vh_ddc\">\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jqm1665703537065.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jqm1665703537065.html\" title=\"Refer to the following table to understand the U9 glyphs that might display.\">U9 Glyphs</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"pje1665703537680.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pje1665703537680.html\" title=\"Refer to the following table to understand the U8 glyphs that might display.\">U8 Glyphs</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mmd1665703538381.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mmd1665703538381.html\" title=\"Refer to the following table to understand the U7 glyphs, listed alphabetically from u7_a* to u7_l*, that might display.\">Glyphs U7: A-L</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kjl1665703539166.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kjl1665703539166.html\" title=\"Refer to the following table to understand the U7 glyphs, listed alphabetically from u7_m* to u7_z*, that might display.\">Glyphs U7: M-Z</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"azy1665703540010.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/azy1665703540010.html\" title=\"Refer to the following table to understand the u_*, ufs_*, and ugfp_* glyphs, that might display.\">Glyphs: u_*, ufs_*, and ugfp_*</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yie1665703540740.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yie1665703540740.html\" title=\"Refer to the tables that group Uniface glyphs by subject or theme. These tables do not include all the glyphs delivered with Uniface.\">Uniface Glyphs by Subject</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534189\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534189\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Uniface Glyphs Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 23, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Uniface delivers a set of glyphs for use in its own tools and editors. New glyphs are added in each new version of Uniface, sometimes replacing older glyphs, sometimes as additions. The following topics list many of the glyphs delivered with Uniface from Uniface 7, 8 and 9. Each topic lists the glyphs alphabetically by name. U9 Glyphs U8 Glyphs Glyphs U7: A-L Glyphs U7: M-Z Glyphs: u_*, ufs_*, and ugfp_* Uniface Glyphs by Subject Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}